Say '''Montevista''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Compostela Valley]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 39,602 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 225 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 8801.	
															
